# AlexStore Backend – Implementation Plan

Backend NestJS + Prisma + MySQL cho dự án AlexStore (e-commerce kiểu Shopee).

## Proposed Changes

---

### Foundation

#### [NEW] `package.json`, `tsconfig.json`, `nest-cli.json`
NestJS project scaffold với các dependencies:
- `@nestjs/core`, `@nestjs/common`, `@nestjs/platform-express`
- `@prisma/client`, `prisma` (dev)
- `@nestjs/jwt`, `@nestjs/passport`, `passport`, `passport-jwt`
- `bcrypt`, `uuid`, `class-validator`, `class-transformer`
- `@nestjs/config`

#### [NEW] `.env.example`
Template biến môi trường: `DATABASE_URL`, `JWT_SECRET`, `JWT_EXPIRES_IN`, `PORT`

#### [NEW] `prisma/schema.prisma`
Full schema dựa trên [database.txt](file:///d:/2A2026/alexstore/alexstore_backend/database.txt):
- Models: `User`, `Category`, `Product`, `ProductImage`, `Cart`, `CartItem`, `Order`, `OrderItem`, `Review`
- `id` dùng `Bytes` (BINARY 16) – UUID v7 sinh ở backend
- Enums: `Role`, `ProductStatus`, `OrderStatus`, `PaymentStatus`
- Index cho các field filter nhiều
- Soft delete với `isDeleted Boolean @default(false)`

#### [NEW] `prisma/migrations/` (first migration)
Chạy `prisma migrate dev --name init`

---

### Core / Shared

#### [NEW] `src/common/uuid.helper.ts`
- `generateUuidV7(): Buffer` – dùng `uuidv7()` từ package `uuidv7`, convert sang Buffer
- `uuidToBuffer(uuid: string): Buffer`
- `bufferToUuid(buf: Buffer): string`

#### [NEW] `src/common/filters/http-exception.filter.ts`
Global exception filter – chuẩn hóa error response:
```json
{ "success": false, "statusCode": 400, "message": "...", "error": "..." }
```

#### [NEW] `src/common/interceptors/response.interceptor.ts`
Global response interceptor – wrap dữ liệu:
```json
{ "success": true, "statusCode": 200, "data": {...} }
```

#### [NEW] `src/common/decorators/roles.decorator.ts`
`@Roles(...roles: Role[])` decorator

#### [NEW] `src/common/guards/jwt-auth.guard.ts`
Guard kiểm tra JWT

#### [NEW] `src/common/guards/roles.guard.ts`
Guard kiểm tra Role từ decorator

---

### Config Module

#### [NEW] `src/config/config.module.ts`
`@nestjs/config` toàn cục – load `.env`

