### Auth Module

#### [NEW] `src/auth/auth.module.ts`
#### [NEW] `src/auth/auth.controller.ts`
- `POST /auth/register`
- `POST /auth/login`

#### [NEW] `src/auth/auth.service.ts`
- `register(dto)`: hash password bcrypt, sinh UUID v7, tạo user
- `login(dto)`: verify password, trả JWT chứa `{ sub, email, role }`

#### [NEW] `src/auth/dto/register.dto.ts`, `login.dto.ts`
