### Order Module (Transaction)

#### [NEW] `src/orders/orders.module.ts`
#### [NEW] `src/orders/orders.controller.ts`
- `POST /orders` (BUYER)
- `GET /orders` (BUYER - lịch sử)
- `GET /orders/:id`
- `PATCH /orders/:id/cancel` (BUYER)
- `PATCH /orders/:id/status` (SELLER/ADMIN)

#### [NEW] `src/orders/orders.service.ts`
`placeOrder()` dùng `prisma.$transaction`:
1. Lock và check product (status=APPROVED, stock>=qty, !isDeleted)
2. Trừ stock
3. Tạo Order với UUID v7
4. Tạo OrderItem
5. Commit

#### [NEW] `src/orders/dto/*.dto.ts`

---

### Review Module (Transaction)

#### [NEW] `src/reviews/reviews.module.ts`
#### [NEW] `src/reviews/reviews.controller.ts`
- `POST /reviews` (BUYER đã mua)
- `GET /reviews?productId=...`

#### [NEW] `src/reviews/reviews.service.ts`
`submitReview()` dùng `prisma.$transaction`:
1. Kiểm tra buyer đã mua sản phẩm
2. Insert review
3. Tính lại avg_rating, review_count
4. Update product

#### [NEW] `src/reviews/dto/*.dto.ts`

---

### App Root

#### [NEW] `src/app.module.ts`
Import tất cả modules, global pipes (ValidationPipe), PrismaModule

#### [NEW] `src/main.ts`
Bootstrap với global exception filter, interceptor, ValidationPipe

#### [NEW] `src/prisma/prisma.module.ts`, `src/prisma/prisma.service.ts`
PrismaService extends PrismaClient, onModuleInit connect

